    "description": "本課程藉由實驗來驗證普通化學課程中之基本原理與定律，讓理論與實驗能相互印證。另一方面訓練學生基本的實驗操作技巧，養成實事求是的科學精神與態度。",
    "prerequisites": "",
    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1. 化學實驗室安全演練<br>2. 實驗室常用器具的操作<br>3. 簡單玻璃細工<br>4. 物質的分離與精製<br>5. 熔點測定<br>6. 固體比重測定<br>7. 化合物化學式的測定<br>8. 質量守恆定律<br>9. 氧的製備與性質<br>10. 二氧化碳的製備與性質<br>11. 氣體體積與溫度關係的驗證<br>12. 硬水檢測與軟化<br>13. 固體溶解度與再結晶<br>14. 膠體溶液性質與凝析<br>",
        "en": "1. Chemistry Laboratory Safety Drill<br>2. Operation of common laboratory equipment<br>3. Simple Glasswork<br>4. Separation and Refinement of Substances<br>5. Melting point determination<br>6. Determination of solid specific gravity<br>7. Determination of chemical formula of compounds<br>8. The law of conservation of mass<br>9. Preparation and Properties of Oxygen<br>10. Preparation and Properties of Carbon Dioxide<br>11. Verification of the relationship between gas volume and temperature<br>12. Hard water detection and softening<br>13. Solid Solubility and Recrystallization<br>14. Colloidal solution properties and coagulation<br>"
    },
